&lt;p&gt;Scale AI is seeking a hands-on &lt;strong&gt;Data Collection Program Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to own and optimize contributor-facing workflows across hardware, rigs, and physical logistics. This role blends program management, operational problem-solving, and process ownership to ensure smooth execution of complex, work stream projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll coordinate contributors, manage hardware and rig logistics, and improve SOPs while solving real-world challenges at the intersection of digital and physical workflows. This role is ideal for someone who thrives in operationally complex environments and wants ownership over end-to-end execution.&lt;/p&gt;
