&lt;li&gt;Track workstreams, identify bottlenecks, and proactively implement solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams (Engineering, Product, Procurement, Data) to ensure seamless execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build reporting and feedback loops to provide transparency and inform leadership decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5 days in office&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
