&lt;li&gt;3–5+ years as a strong Operations or Program Manager with exposure to hardware, logistics, or physical workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience coordinating multiple work streams simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on problem solver with a bias toward action&lt;/li&gt;
